# Claude Code — Global Context for [Your Name]

This file is loaded into every session. Tech stack, projects, and conventions are in `~/.claude/rules/`.

---

## Dispatch Protocol

Use `/cast <request>` to break any task into specialist agent work. This is the primary way to delegate.
Use specific commands (`/plan`, `/debug`, `/test`, `/commit`, etc.) when you know the exact agent needed.

**Inline only for:** reading code, answering questions, short analysis, <5 line edits.
**Token rule:** If haiku can handle it, dispatch haiku — not sonnet/opus.

