### Config

- **Rules:** `~/.claude/rules/` — stack-context, project-catalog, working-conventions
- **Agents:** `~/.claude/agents/`
- **Plans:** `~/.claude/plans/`
- **Agent memory:** `~/.claude/agent-memory-local/<agent-name>/`
- **Skills:** `~/.claude/skills/` — calendar-fetch, inbox-fetch, reminders-fetch, git-activity, action-items, briefing-writer, careful-mode, freeze-mode, wizard
- **Output dirs:** `~/.claude/briefings/`, `~/.claude/meetings/`, `~/.claude/reports/`
